WEBVTT

00:02:28.500 --> 00:02:30.809
and particularly the United States,

00:02:30.833 --> 00:02:32.434
was a huge supporter --

00:02:32.458 --> 00:02:33.851
and funder --

00:02:33.875 --> 00:02:36.934
of the global polio
eradication initiative.

00:02:36.958 --> 00:02:38.458
They had their reasoning.

00:02:39.667 --> 00:02:42.518
That lack of trust,

00:02:42.542 --> 00:02:46.018
that "just a rumor or two"

00:02:46.042 --> 00:02:52.184
cost the polio eradication program
500 million dollars

00:02:52.208 --> 00:02:53.851
to reset the clock,

00:02:53.875 --> 00:02:57.976
to regain the progress lost
during those 11 months

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.393
and beyond.

00:02:59.417 --> 00:03:05.518
The Nigerian strain of the polio virus
traveled to over 20 countries,